    "learnmode": {
      "image": "/drivers/diy_custom_zigbee/assets/learnmode.svg",
      "instruction": {
        "en": "DIY Custom Zigbee Device (PTVO, ESP32-H2, CC2530, etc.)\n\n1. Put your DIY device in pairing mode\n2. For PTVO: Short press the button or power cycle\n3. For ESP32: Follow your firmware instructions\n4. For CC2530/CC2531: Power cycle or use button\n5. Device will be auto-detected\n\nSupported Firmware:\n- PTVO Configurable Firmware\n- ESP Zigbee SDK (ESP32-H2/C6)\n- DIYRuZ projects\n- Tasmota Zigbee\n- Custom ZCL implementations",
        "fr": "Appareil Zigbee DIY (PTVO, ESP32-H2, CC2530, etc.)\n\n1. Mettez votre appareil DIY en mode appairage\n2. PTVO: Appui court sur le bouton ou redémarrage\n3. ESP32: Suivez les instructions de votre firmware\n4. CC2530/CC2531: Redémarrage ou bouton\n5. L'appareil sera auto-détecté\n\nFirmwares Supportés:\n- PTVO Configurable Firmware\n- ESP Zigbee SDK (ESP32-H2/C6)\n- Projets DIYRuZ\n- Tasmota Zigbee\n- Implémentations ZCL personnalisées"
      }
    }
